{"header":"<h1>Module <code><span>Bv_values.Typed</span></code></h1>","type":"documentation","uses_katex":false,"breadcrumbs":[{"name":"Index","href":"../../../../index.html","kind":"leaf-page"},{"name":"soteria","href":"../../../index.html","kind":"page"},{"name":"Soteria","href":"../../index.html","kind":"module"},{"name":"Bv_values","href":"../index.html","kind":"module"},{"name":"Typed","href":"#","kind":"module"}],"toc":[],"source_anchor":null,"preamble":"","content":"<div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec module-type anchored\" id=\"module-type-S\"><a href=\"#module-type-S\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">module</span> <span class=\"keyword\">type</span> <a href=\"module-type-S/index.html\">S</a></span><span> = <span class=\"keyword\">sig</span> ... <span class=\"keyword\">end</span></span></code></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec module anchored\" id=\"module-Make_transparent\"><a href=\"#module-Make_transparent\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">module</span> <a href=\"Make_transparent/index.html\">Make_transparent</a></span><span> (<a href=\"Make_transparent/argument-1-V/index.html\">V</a> : <a href=\"../Svalue/module-type-Value_ext/index.html\">Svalue.Value_ext</a>) () : <span class=\"keyword\">sig</span> ... <span class=\"keyword\">end</span></span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p>Like <a href=\"Make/index.html\"><code>Make</code></a>, but additionally exposes the ghost-typed <code>+'a t</code>/<code>+'a ty</code> as transparently equal to the underlying untyped svalue. This lets a downstream module write extension helpers without juggling <code>type_</code>/<code>untyped</code>/<code>cast</code>, while its own <code>.mli</code> re-seals <code>t</code>/<code>ty</code> as abstract for the rest of the world.</p></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec module anchored\" id=\"module-Make\"><a href=\"#module-Make\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">module</span> <a href=\"Make/index.html\">Make</a></span><span> (<a href=\"Make/argument-1-V/index.html\">V</a> : <a href=\"../Svalue/module-type-Value_ext/index.html\">Svalue.Value_ext</a>) () : <a href=\"module-type-S/index.html\">S</a> <span class=\"keyword\">with</span> <span><span class=\"keyword\">module</span> <a href=\"module-type-S/Ext/index.html\">Ext</a> = <a href=\"Make/argument-1-V/index.html\">V</a></span></span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p>The main entry point of <code>Bv_values</code>. Builds the <em>ghost-typed</em> svalue layer over <a href=\"../Svalue/Make/index.html\"><code>Svalue.Make</code></a>: the same hash-consed values, but exposed through a phantom-typed <code>+'a t</code> whose <code>'a</code> tracks each value's kind (the <code>sint</code>, <code>sbool</code>, <code>sptr</code>, ... tags) so that ill-kinded combinations are rejected at compile time. The result also bundles the matching <code>Svalue</code> (untyped layer), <code>Eval</code> (normalisation) and <code>Expr</code> (substitution) modules.</p></div></div>"}